data.meta_description: With special guest, Corbette Jackson! Kip Moore splashed into the mainstream with the double-Platinum "Somethin' 'Bout a Truck" in 2012, then followed up with three more bestselling #1s ("Hey Pretty Girl,” "Beer Money," and "More Girls Like You"), a trio of ambitious, critically acclaimed albums and two gritty EPs.
